    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Breakout》回归！Choice Provisions（《Bit.Trip》系列的开发商） 颠覆了这一传奇系列游戏。在这款经典游戏的霓虹版本中，通过清除砖块来解开每个谜题，达到最终目标。游玩时间越长，连击次数与特效强度就会越高，让人眼花缭乱的视听盛宴是对最熟练玩家莫大的犒赏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/32fabcb79f08398d9d6784c8aa5ee740.poster.avif?t=1742910286\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/32fabcb79f08398d9d6784c8aa5ee740.webm?t=1742910286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/32fabcb79f08398d9d6784c8aa5ee740.mp4?t=1742910286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊方块助你一臂之力，比如能清除砖块的大爆炸、能救球的挡板以及能洞穿所有砖块的激光炮。每一种方块都会为玩家带来令人眼花缭乱的动态效果，创造出《Breakout》中前所未有的惊险刺激。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/e0ed8b4f9091c479f0b4e536669fcf43.poster.avif?t=1742910286\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/e0ed8b4f9091c479f0b4e536669fcf43.webm?t=1742910286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/e0ed8b4f9091c479f0b4e536669fcf43.mp4?t=1742910286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >72 个关卡考验你的技巧，但你并非孤立无援。“专注模式”下，你可以减慢游戏时间，但得分也会相应降低。如果想和好友一同游戏，你可以在本地双人合作模式中叫上伙伴一起闯关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/8ba193d4cc7e3a1703492ca0ab63345d.poster.avif?t=1742910286\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041770/extras/8ba193d4cc7e3a1703492ca0ab63345d.webm?t=1742910286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 72 个关卡挑战你击破砖块的技巧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 可解锁无限模式，在全球联网的排行榜中一竞高下</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 可与好友在双人合作模式中畅玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 由程序生成的音频与视觉效果，会随连击增多而不断叠加</p>",
